Class AbstractPreference

java.lang.Object
  pluginlib.AbstractPreference
Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractPreference.BooleanOption, AbstractPreference.ChoiceOption, AbstractPreference.StringOption
public class AbstractPreference
extends java.lang.Object

This is a base class for persistent options. The options are stored as workspace preferences.

Author:
David R. Cok
